# --- BTG AEGIS DEPLOYMENT ENV ---

# Required for AI Features (SIGINT/OSINT/ORACLE)
# Get a key from https://aistudio.google.com/
GEMINI_API_KEY="YOUR_GEMINI_API_KEY"

# APP_URL: The URL where this applet is hosted.
# In Vercel, this is automatically handled, but you can set it if needed.
APP_URL="YOUR_DEPLOYED_URL"

# Note for Vercel:
# In the Vercel Dashboard, go to Settings -> Environment Variables.
# Add 'GEMINI_API_KEY' as a secret.
# The app is configured to automatically pick up this key during build via vite.config.ts.
